page.title: 19LIFE STYLES
page.content: My name is Maria Farress. I am seven years old. In my spare time I enjoy { {reading, playing with my dolls}and{ {riding my bike.}Sometimes I play {tennis}with my brother. I am a{Brownie.}At{Brownies}we learn many things and play games with lots of my friends. We work to earn{badges. It is really good fun. I go to{ballet}and{tap}for two and a half hours a week. We do a show twice a year when our parents and grandparents come to see us perform. At the{weekend}we often go to{Burnham} to{walk}by the river. We come home and eat a delicious{roast dinner cooked by my Mum. Another thing I enjoy doing is going to the{library}because I can borrow {books.
